---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Internal SLA Dashboard" description="Internal operational ticket dashboard.">
  <section class="kharon-container py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Internal SLA Dashboard</h1>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-slate-600">
      This dashboard is the internal operational layer for triage submissions, SLA routing, and ticket visibility.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="border border-[var(--color-line)] bg-white p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-700">Emergency</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">High-priority SLA failures and technical escalation.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-[var(--color-line)] bg-white p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Engineering</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">New builds, upgrades, and system design intake.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-[var(--color-line)] bg-white p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Maintenance</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">PPM, audits, lifecycle maintenance, and service scheduling.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>